snippet.title: Official Trailer | Call of Duty: Warzone
snippet.description:
#Warzone.

Free to play for everyone.
Drop in tomorrow. 

Explore Verdansk, bring home the money in Plunder, or fight until no one else stands in your way in Battle Royale. #FreeCallofDuty

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
Twitter: http://twitter.com/CallofDuty
Instagram: http://instagram.com/callofduty
Facebook: http://facebook.com/CallofDuty
